    "patch_code": "public double[] repairAndDecode(final double[] x) {\n    double[] bounds = getBounds();\n    for (int i = 0; i < x.length; ++i) {\n        while (!isFeasible(i)) {\n            final double lowerBound = bounds[2 * i];\n            final double upperBound = bounds[2 * i + 1];\n            \n            // Ensure the values within the bounds\n            x[i] = Math.max(lowerBound, Math.min(upperBound, x[i]));\n        }\n    }\n    \n    return decode(x);\n}",
